    "body": "@metachris I looked at the relay implementation and there is no way to avoid having a payout by setting up proposer feeRecipient as coinbase address, It runs a check to ensure that the last TX is a payout TX.\r\nA requirement to have a payout TX complicated a few things and is really just inefficient.\r\n\r\nInstead of this payout, the relay can use other methods for tracking and analytics.",
